623	
624	
625	\leanok
626	  Compose three isomorphisms: the terminal-collapse of Yoneda, the constancy isomorphism after whiskering with the free functor, and the identification of the free module on a singleton with \(k\) itself. Then apply sheafification.
627	\end{proof}
